W&B Registry

Once you have logged your checkpoints to Artifacts, you can then register your best model checkpoints and centralize them across your team with [Registry](/models/registry). Using Registry, you can organize your best models by task, manage the lifecycles of models, track and audit the entire ML lifecycle, and [automate](/models/automations) downstream actions. To link a model Artifact, refer to [Registry](/models/registry).

